          <p class="mt-2 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-pretty text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 sm:text-5xl lg:text-balance">Reparaciones</p>
          <p class="mt-6 text-lg/8 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-100">Algunas de las reparaciones más comunes que realizamos son:</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl sm:mt-20 lg:mt-24 lg:max-w-4xl">
          <dl class="grid max-w-xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-10 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-y-16">
            <div class="relative pl-16">
              <dt class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
                <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 flex size-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-accent">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20.25px" height="27px" viewBox="0 0 384 512"><path fill="#ffffff" d="M16 64C16 28.7 44.7 0 80 0h224c35.3 0 64 28.7 64 64v384c0 35.3-28.7 64-64 64H80c-35.3 0-64-28.7-64-64zm208 384a32 32 0 1 0-64 0a32 32 0 1 0 64 0m80-384H80v320h224z"/></svg>
